name: Ozmodeus
description: In the vast web's woven threads, where many eyes do roam, They stop, they stare, they choose to care, or pass by like a poem. For every post that's shared in jest, or tale that's told with glee, There's a choice to make, a path to take, in this digital sea. You've been a beacon, long and bright, in this online land, A fixture here, year after year, with humor close at hand. So when a soul, with time to troll, decides to cast a stone, Remember well, it's their choice to dwell, on the seeds you've sown. For every word, both seen and heard, is a mirror of the mind, And what we seek, in peak or bleak, is a reflection of our kind. So stand your ground, with joy you've found, and let the trolls pass by, For in this space, it's your grace, that truly will defy.

Cuando no estoy sumergido en mi trabajo, me encanta pasar tiempo al aire libre, ya sea explorando senderos naturales, practicando deportes o simplemente disfrutando de un picnic en el parque. También disfruto de las noches tranquilas en casa, viendo una película acogedora o leyendo un buen libro.

name: uniguy1
description:
First off- I look at a woman in a relationship as a PARTNER. 
Partners.. you do not cheat, or beat or lie too.
I like women who are strong.. or even more so when they want to achieve strength and are looking to be shown this!! NOW in all that, I still understand that the thing women wish to hear above I LOVE YOU.. is I WILL TAKE CARE OF YOU !

I have been told that I have had (and still do) an extremely interesting life- which, I guess, makes me a bit of an interesting guy;. You may feel the same after reading this rather long monologue.
Someone like myself is a very different male. I act different. I treat women as complete equals and do what I can to build up, support someone .. ONCE I KNOW that they are truly in honest reveal and present for me. This does happen long distance.. or months of letters, chat and skype !!!!!!!!! This happens in person, after they are convinced of me and of them. Whatever I ask for them, I will already be prepared to do for them, if I haven't already. 
SEX ! ? ! .. not interested in it being used as some link chain fence or weapon. I am not easily swayed. I would expect any woman worth herself; to be looking at all opportunities.. until.. I am sitting at a restaurant table, in her town.. and she has true, sober opportunity to size her and us & see as if we would be a good fit, no matter what paddle was exchanged electronically. It does not sound like it so far.. but I am a big romantic .. I live history, I adore strong women-(or ones that want to become such), I am a conservative- a constitutionalist.. the exact opposite of socialist and fascist! Being very tactile.. romance and sex are an art and pleasurable past-time with high importance-- BUT again.. not a weapon.
I intend to be located Globally.. in a few residences.. Islands- off Panama, Caribbeans, Azores, Southern France and THE Mediterranean... somewhere in that mix. I intend to travel the globe in an adventurous search for health treatments and age-extending methods-places like the Blue Zones!
I am in extremely good health.. healthy now than when I was in my 30's!.. and getting a bit younger here and there. In person.. most think I am in my early 50s..with effort, I can take another 5+ years off that. (secrets). 

My travels will reveal a gift I can give the world.. anyway.. this is my goal. I do not believe in Dreams for myself-(Others can have wasted days with theirs)- I believe in goals. I love that women from Eastern Europe-ie: Ukraine, Czech Rep. ect... do and accomplish more than protest and complain.. this is very unlike American women.. hence, why.. someone like yourself, from where you are from are reading this.
BUT, 1st.. to be fair to myself, I must reveal that I have extreme sensitivity to cat dander and Lies.
The Dander I can take a pill for.. but will not.
-- LIES (!!).. not so much- there is no pill!. I have had people lie and lie to me my whole life. And, again, to be fair.. I let them, never letting them know that I KNOW.. till I put an end to them/their evil/ the relationships/acquaintances. It is some kind of weird, netherworld type gift.. OR GOD just gives me clues-- clues that are so affirming-like a big bug crawling across your face. Whatever the source- it IS REAL.
In the past, my ego or nativity has cost me dearly!!! That all stopped about 15 years ago. 
I have never been one for getting compliments-giving YES.. receiving - NO! On these websites.. I expect a woman to be talking to a number of men.. and even be on multiple sites.. BUT such lying about obvious things - - would make such individuals dust to me without explanation.
I have resources which aide me in such info.
Even if someone claims that they have never been close or in a relationship- ERGO, A Virgin.. this can be held to the light of truth and found out!
I tend to be a self-contained person.. again.. unusual for many of the weak minded Westerners. THANK YOU .. I NEEDED TO STATE ALL THAT SO THE LIARS CAN GO ELSEWHERE.. To Clarify.. I actually live in a SAFE area North of Chicago.

name: ReneAuces
description:
Me gusta dar abrazos, me gusta sonreír a todo el mundo incluso si me caen en parte mal. No me gusta la falsedad, ni las mentiras. Odio las personas que se creen superiores a los demás o a las que se creen que con un chasquido de dedos van a tener todo hecho. Siempre me ha gustado luchar por lo que quiero y me he encontrado con muchos obstáculos que no pude derribar, piedras que me hacían tropezar y personas que me dificultaban el paso.
Tengo mis fallos, como todo el mundo. No soy perfecta, no hay nadie que lo sea. Me falla el que a veces mido mucho las palabras y no llego a decir lo que en verdad pienso. Me fallan bromas de mal gusto y a destiempo. Me falla esa cabezonería que tengo. Me falla que, a veces, no sé cual es el momento adecuado para decir lo siento y otras ni si quiera me atrevo o no me sale de dentro. Y otras muchas cosas más..
Siempre me suelo valorar menos de lo que en verdad valgo por temor a que piense algo incierto. Soy algo insegura.
Sonrío porque ya he llorado bastante. es lo más fácil que hay, por eso sonrío, para que nadie piense que voy a lo fácil o que soy muy débil

name: Ntwadumela
description:
I grew up in MT and WY and moved to Colorado in 2003. I left again in 2016 and came back in 2020.

My family consists of some cousins who live in Wyoming.

I thought this pandemic might have been over by now, but it isn't. It just keeps coming at you every day.

I have been working at home since March 2020. It has its advantages, but I miss the social interaction.

I like doing a variety of activities or watching. I checked those off on my interests and they're listed on my profile.

I have bad knees due to sports injuries during my youth. Therefore, if you're looking for an outdoorsy woman who can go hiking, skiing, etc., I'm afraid you will have to continue your search.

I'm not perfect and I'm not looking for perfection. Just honesty, straightforwardness and a good sense of humor. You must live in the Denver area or close by. I don't do long distance relationships.

FYI: I will NOT download Chat Apps on my cell phone. My Facebook App got hacked and it cost me a lot of time, money and grief to fix it.

If you are against talking on the phone, move on please. That is the only way I'm going to communicate if you don't want to continue talking on POF.

Make it a great day!

description:
I like to consider myself someone who can relate to anyone and any culture and background. It allows me to make very personal connections with everyone I meet. I have a quick wit and love to laugh about everything under the sun. 
I like travel, tennis, read books, sewing clothing, painting by numbers, play with my dog, spend time with parents and friends, sport Pilates, cooking yummy food and bake cupcakes, i like two candles on a table good music and deep conversations.
I am looking for a genuine mental connection, a real relationship with someone special, I am interested in quality, not quantity, I value thoughtful and passionated people with great conversational skills and good sense of humor.
I’m looking for a partner in crime to make some great memories. Chemistry is really the only thing that matters to me. Trips, dinners, etc are always better with the right person. Wouldn’t you agree? 
If you have arrived on my profile you can continue reading you will like it , if you don’t then anyways I won’t know. LOL
Well pleasure, fun, happiness and deep experiences we all seek. I look to create together some Fun filled, good times , enjoyable deep conversations, long walks and mutual pleasure .
Indeed all of this with su** to it , hmm I guess that does make a good package.
Enjoying life and love to travel, seeing what the world has to offer. The world is a book and those who do not travel, read only a page! 
Live every minute of my life like it is the last one, very optimistic hunger of life ... no excuses and travel with no regrets. 
The grass is greener where you water it ... so we must take control of your life and start watering our own pastures and grow our own greener grasses. The universe is always seeking balance. 
My goal in life is Happiness, Harmony, Peace, Traveling discover the world. I'd like to think that I am half way there. I am grateful to be alive! 
You only live once, but if you do it right, once is enough! 
I wish you all success in your search!

name: walt3rg
description:
Have you ever MET a simple and confident man who loves animals and is filled with an incredible passion for life? So here I am; An intelligent and interesting person, who really wants to share everything exciting with someone good in life, in this amazing world. I am very serious in my search and I have things clear, loyalty, love and above all mutual understanding is the most important thing in a relationship. I am a generous man with great passion for details, and clear feelings.

So I describe myself as... An open-minded, generous and enterprising man! I am full of love! I always smile, even if I am in a bad mood or it is better to say that I am only in a good mood because our life is for fun and not for sadness. I like walking, the sea and nature, it is the only way to relax and be calm, the afternoons reading a book and listening to music are one of my great passions! I know how to cook and I am always willing to learn something new. I also like my job, which is design, it's very exciting, traveling to discover new places and I really hope to find my half, to be able to be part of it and want to form a good relationship. We can build what we want and what we want if we know exactly.

A few simple words for the amazing person I hope to find on this site...

I have no idea where I'm going
nor where destiny takes me from.
But I want you to be by my side.

You will be the best written page;
That my destiny has written in my life,
And now I know I was not wrong.

and without hesitation I would give you everything,
And if it didn't exist, I would invent it.

With you I want to grow old.
With you there are plenty of wishes,
I don't ask for more because you are everything I long for,
and if it's with you I'll stay

It is a privilege to have you in my life,
That just seeing you makes my day,
And forever, I want to have you.

there will be no barriers to love you,
because being together,
the universe will be in favor
and everything will be perfect.
I will enjoy your kisses
I will be a fan of your body and the passion you give me.
It will be a pleasure to have you every day in my calendar.
and everything will be easier because you will be with me my love.

Blessings

Por lo tanto solo personas serias y que tengan claro lo que quieren y lo que NO quieren para su vida futura.


Entonces si quieres una relación seria y estable con amor comprensión y respeto, estaré encantado de entrar en comunicación contigo.

Hasta pronto


Ernesto Giraldo

name: Carter_Keyes
description:
Surely You have been asked, 'Is your glass half empty , or are you a half full kinda girl? Me, I say 'It's the wrong freakin' glass altogether! I mean forget the whole 'Grass is Greener Syndrome'. I tend to deny the other side even has grass until I've mowed My own lawn into a pulp'. Now that doesn't make Me a cynic, I'm a realist. I simply look for a more sound and logical solution for any issue.

A little about Me in general, I'm a proud graduate form Kansas State with an earned degree in Policy Management. That doesn't elevate me to being the smartest or quickest guy in the room, or better than those less formally educated than I, this is merely a fact of My achievement and part of My success in life. I am a decorated combat veteran of the U.S. Air Force and proudly support all troops, soldiers, and military men and women in all their work regardless of the party politics. But 'Who' I am is what I'll tell you the most...

Me, I am always the one focused on having exact change for the bus while others are jostling for either an isle or window seat. That's Me, always on top of it. Not once have I ever left someone without toilet paper, or force them to use napkins or other random products that happen to within arm's reach of the toilet. Oh no, I've always anticipated when we'll need something. You can always rely on Me to make the journey smoother. Reliability is a tremendous quality you'll have never appreciated until meeting Me! But now that you've tasted it, you will find it indispensable. Being with Me will give You a certain peace of mind you'll have never experienced before, an ability to not worry about taking care of the world around you at all times, simply because YOU are now being taken care of as well.

I have been to the mountain top and possessed the 'Golden Goose'. I've also been swept from it's perch , committed my sins and atoned for my crimes with parole papers in hand. I've been left and abandoned. Experienced homelessness, grown heartless and have become a better man for it. This isn't about where I've been, or who I used to be, but more where I am now and where I will go next.

So know this, if you want to get inspired, feel desired and be held in honor and know that you are valued? If you want your 'Jerry McGuire' moment? Then get on your knees and demand to be served a bottomless glass of me. Throw your head back and be consumed by my intoxicating Elixir! I can promise you this: hangovers are guaranteed and a party there will always be. Non-stop. So come on, jump on in, the waters fine. I got You.

There you have it, a cursory introduction to the man I am, and the friend I vow to become. I don't 'Spit Game' and I'm no 'G', nor am I a 'Killer', but don't push Me,. I'm a protector, a valued asset. I stand My ground and I'm not afraid to spill blood in honor of a cause for My friends in defense of race, religion, or even stupidity.

I'm seeking a 'Soldier' to march beside Me. A steadfast lighthouse within the calm of every storm. I am today, I am tomorrow and I am unwavering. What I tell you today, is how I will feel tomorrow. I am open to conversation and debate and of course My feelings can be persuaded to different views and standings. I just don't change My mind with the direction of the wind. Make an argument and back it up with facts. I will listen. I am open to change, just not false posturing.

I look forward to reading Your words in reply, viewing your script. Don't be timid, venture any question to me as there is nothing I won't entertain or tell, given only that You ask. Surely you have them, questions? Nothing is to absurd or edgy. From this moment on, just let it begin....

I am really curious to see this site and to 'see' how it's supposed to go, lol! I am here for friends only at the moment. name: Patybelabrasil
description:
Well trying describe about ourselves I can say it is a little bit complicated but I will try it. I have graduated in Languages Art, Iam English, Portuguese and literature teacher. I speak my mother language portuguese, english, spanish and also sign language, I used to work with deaf kids too.
For me to be a teacher is an honorable job, because I know I can make a difference in someone’s life. In some reason, I still studying english language because some dayI wanna become a translator, and work as interpreter . 
Actually, people used to say that: I am very kindheart and positive girl because most at all the times I try to seening the best of life regardless of the ircumstances or situation by which I think that what is always teach us a positive lesson. 
Of coruse I could tell I have many flaws, but I know life is worth the struggle when I look back on what I lost and realize that what I have now is much greater. 
I do not like talking to with somebody behave as a “drama King”, or complain about their personal problems all the time, please, everybody has problems, just try solving it in your best way or attempt to learn how to deal with it, and live your life the best way because our lives is too short and we did not know what the future has prepared for each one of us. Sometimes we are so much selfish with ourselves and forget that has many people around the world living in the worse situation starving, homeless and They are just begging to have a little dignity to live. Well unfortunately, I cannot save the world but at least think about those people and stopping complain about what I had earned in my life.
I also ejoying my life keeping studying, reading, watching a great movie, listening to 80’s music, ice skating, animals, the nature, go to camping, to do volunteer jobs and talking about all sorts of issues even politics, even if we do not have the same point of view, I like to keep my brain work out all the time, in the matter of fact in my opinion "Education is the key to success in life, and teachers can make a lasting impact in the lives of their students." 
I am from Brazil, I live by myself since I was 17 years, I am harder worker and independent woman, I already have my own place, that it is already payed off. For me being in this website, I will be very straightforward, I am here in this page, because I wanna practicing my english skills and also I believe that has someone very “kindheart and humble” out there waiting to give an opportunity to know each other, and maybe, we become a great friends and work out together. 
I really would like to clear something up, and be very honest about to be here in this site: I AM NOT here in this page to ask men to pay my bills, send me money, or rescue me, because I live in a poor country. and I am not desperate to move into your country for me to get a free, easy and best life.
A I have already told, I’m self-sufficient woman and “I DO NOT NEED MAN TO PAY IT OR THAT FOR ME” because I can get by myself as well. what I can say more about me is I am as well world traveled, and I have been different places in Europe for many times, also I've lived in Texas- USA for a few years, if I would like to have had a easy and good life with a richer man, believe me, I could already done it because I had many opportunities before but I prefer to believe that the older values my mother had taught me is the best way to get success in life and mainly in love. My grandfather always used to tell me to be honest with myself first, and” treat people they way you would like to be treated”.
Well I think I had said enough about myself. I hope you all could like my profile and I had tryied as much as I could be honest!!

name: AlejandroGuti
description:
I love to write, because writings can travel further than anything; they cross the seas and times, they go deep into the thought, they produce infinite smiles and tears that free the soul or make it prey of memories. Poetry sometimes looks old-fashioned in this world, but it touches the soul with such softness that it seems to caress the hearts. 
Hobbies Photography, music, videogames; i read so much, i like climbing, camping, traveling, walking, writing. 
Me encanta escribir. pienso que los escritos pueden viajar más lejos que cualquier otra cosa; cruzan los mares y los tiempos, se adentran en el pensamiento, producen infinitas sonrisas y lágrimas que liberan el alma o la hacen presa de los recuerdos. La poesía a veces parece pasada de moda en este mundo, pero toca el alma con tal suavidad que parece acariciar los corazones. 
Aficiones Fotografía, música, video juegos; leo mucho, me gusta escalar, acampar, viajar, caminar, escribir.

name: LionsFaith7
description:
Hi there thanks for taking the time to read my profile. My name is Daniel and I'm currently a student at Berkeley college and my major is criminal justice. I’m working towards an Associates degree in cyber security. I’m an honor student and been doing very well in my classes.

When I’m not studying I’m spending time with my family and my little dog. A good friend of mine told me that family is important and I totally agree. I love my natural family and I also love my spiritual family. I’m a Christian man who loves his Lord and savior Jesus Christ. I’m not a perfect man and I try to do my best because that is all I can do. I have many things I enjoy like going places and seeing interesting things. I moved here to New Jersey from California four years ago. I was always out on my off days going along the coast and stopping by at one of my favorite hangouts to eat and have a nice hot cup of tea. I love going to little cafes and supporting mom and pop businesses. 

I enjoy listening to music and coming from a Puerto Rican family we love our music. I have a few family members who are Jazz musicians and one played with famous performers. My music taste is very picky and at the moment I’m listening to 70s, 80s and EDM music. One of my hobbies is collecting vintage electronics such as a music device called NET MD (MiniDisc). I included a picture if it in my profile. I'm a tech nerd and I get fascinated in the history and the workings of technology. I hope to someday with my lady by my side go tech hunting together at flea markets and thrift shops, another favorite fun past time of mine to do.

I hope to someday find a woman who will accept me for me inside and out. A woman who will love me unconditionally. I'm willing to date and take this slow so we can learn about each other. If all goes well it will someday lead to marriage. I find women who have colored streaks in their hair very attractive.

description: I guess as they say you have to jump in with both feet but I am not sure exactly where to start. I am new to this dating/friendship thing. Fortunately, I was aware of this site and scammers so I knew where not to go. I am looking to meet people and make friends around the world and locally if possible. Maybe I will find someone special maybe not but it is more important to have friends and someone to converse with than I do now. I did not realize how small my world had become until I escaped. Now, I look forward to the new life I am recreating and the joy I have in regrowing a new garden along with a new life and friendships. I am a Paramedic and I teach high schoolers to be EMT's which can be a daunting task during the COVID times as I call them. I also deployed to NYC last March for 60 days. That was an adventure but not one I care to repeat. I figure at this point in life I am beyond the point of playing games with anyone. If you want to know more or would like to know more just ask. Like I tell my students I can be very blunt but you will never hear a lie.

name: Ghost69
description:
About Me: Credibility means EVERYTHING!

I’ve always been highly intuitive, simply put, I don’t see the world the same way most do. Depending on what you believe, some would say I’m an empath. I have always been a human lie detector and can sense things in my surroundings such as the way a dog may sense danger in a person. 

When I was attending dealing school, one of the instructors who had been in casino surveillance over 30yrs insisted that I consider going into surveillance. Observing me he said “when the game is in play, I noticed that while everyone else is looking at the table, you’re analyzing it and breaking things down. You just don’t look at things and process them the same as most, it’s much more advanced”.

Fighting For the Little Guys

6yrs ago I started an advocacy against slave labor in the Philippines 

After reaching 30,000 members I created our Non Profit Organization - Filipino Goodwill ESL which can best be described as a Independent Contractors Union to negotiate their contracts for them, legally represent them, we offer further training, mentorship programs, and emergency relief fund as well as job security. 



Scammer Busters

QUOTED FROM MY GROUP:
“One might wonder what makes me think that I am able to learn or find anything out,
Or what kind of experience do I have in such matters of recon-ing information on People or schools? 

We would have to go back to 2010 when I did it pretty much as a
Hobby under an entity named "Scammer Buster". This was an incognito account that I created to catch scammers who were cheating people in my online selling groups in
The Philippines. It grew to a point where I had to make a group to hold public trials.

I dug, found evidence, phone numbers, alias names, witnesses and victims. I would compile the info, post it as a file [case] in the group, then invite the accused, present
The file and ask them how they plead, guilty or innocent? It was amazing how much attention that got, I literally made everyone who was guilty famous, and they couldn't turn anywhere to sell anything in the Philippines without somebody knowing who they were & that forced them to have to close their accounts and start all over. Being a vigilante is kind of in my blood I guess. Now, for those who may think I'm
Exaggerating? Here's a home page of a site that recorded everything”
Scammers Busted

I get home from work to a big quiet house... i hate being single. I feed my 2 pretty white kittens, then i feed my Seahorses. I spend about an hour reading to my fans on YouTube, then i crawl into my big comfy bed and fall asleep to Netflix. 

On my days off i like to go for walks, drive my nice car, and relax in my hot tub or grill on my deck... 

If you think you would like to hang out with me, or can help me with having to do all this stuff alone, please message me, i really miss having someone to come home to. someone to cook for, and someone to spoil.

name: Richie_valentin
description:
I know i do not have a profile picture, as most can be fake therefore its better we get to know each other and eventually we shall see each other, a person does not come dressed in red cape But as everything you have ever wished for… This is me, I am most passionate about, taking care of others, helping people, and making people smile. Yes, I know that sounds cheesy but I try really hard to brighten the day of everyone I meet, even if it’s just by asking a cashier how they are or holding the door open for someone. I try to always think about that quote by the Dalai Lama: ‘Be kind whenever possible. It is always possible. ’ Hello girls thanks for stopping by. I’m a creative, fun-loving, energetic and active BOY or shall i say Man, whose favourite words in any language are ‘Please proceed to your gate for departure’. I’ve been bitten HARD by the travel bug lol.. . and have been lucky enough to visit every continent (well, I’m working on most. I love going out, meeting new people and generally getting the most out of life whether that’s trying new bars and restaurants or picking up a new sport, love swimming, running, jogging and, oh yes i love my sports i am a martial artist, love combat, the art of self defense as one of my favourite quote by bruce lee ‘As you think, and shall you become’. BUT girls i adore, i respect and worship like the angels, i am soft like the petal of rose and when it comes to womens i can smell the fragrance from milestones, my knee trembles, body shakes, heart beeps and my hormones grow, the taste of cherry rows and their looks are like the ablazing stars that how i feel when it comes to women, But i also believe beauty is not through the apparel that decorates us, true beauty is from knowledge and manners. So looks are partly important but substances are what decorates us!!! . I love nature and animals, astrology has always been an inspiration to me and spirituality is another but what determines a person's success is the belief he instills and keeps working towards his goals until he reaches the true destination of his existence which will determine the total outcome of the desired result. I love reading various books and do not have any particular taste anything that interests me from a sentence might flow through my veins, reading brings knowledge and knowledge is power, the power to know and learn and understand but also the power to dream, stories inspire us to reach high, love deep above all every book allows us to dream a new dream! ! I love solving puzzles and also love playing chess at times, although i have not played for a while, i love creative cooking and being active with house works. I love comedy show movies, and love historical series as such my favorite ‘KURULUS OSMAN’. I never mentioned at the beginning of my sentence that yes, by life I am a business oriented person more like an entrepreneur. I travelled to various countries and conducted business relationships, I do not worship money but I respect the value it holds. Money does partially motivate me but above all a rabbit hole is what distinguishes me. Walls are created of steel and now I am on the bridge gazing at the star where my journey begins, a rose that grew out of concrete…. .

I am looking for a person whos admired for who she is, not just her shiny necklaces or designer shoes but she is creative thinks for herself and speaks her mind, down to earth open to exposures and love to experiment different dimensions I’m definitely looking for someone who is in love with life and open to exploring all its possibilities. Travel is a really big part of my life and I’d love to meet someone who wants to join me on my many adventures. I’d definitely like to start a family one day, so I’m looking for a girl who’d also like to raise a couple of beautiful, multilingual, adventurous kids well just a saying but let's see. You should shoot me a message if you’re fun-loving, and up for anything and we shall see where our journey begins. .

name: HurtDad5150
description:
I cannot imagine how many times I’ve attempted to fill out one of these ‘profile’ things on an app.

It seems like every attempt I make the contents of what I enter disappear just as quickly as the website transfers me to their “you must join to be a member” site and the half hour it took to enter real information about myself is lost with that transfer.

The truth is this:

I’m an EX- Marine, a veteran who despised himself for serving a system that turned out to be anything BUT being service to his country.

I’ve been married, twice, and both times the marriage failed because I was incapable of allowing anyone to actually love me.

The fact that I knew love, once and a very long time ago makes finding real love again a task I see as being nearly impossible. 

I will finish my first full length book, an autobiographical/ self help book that I hope might help others avoid some of the mistakes I have made over the years and upon its publication I intend (if Europe ever allows Americans to travel there in spite of the Covid-19 pandemic) to leave immediately before it publishes or as soon after as I possibly can.

My intent and purpose for backpacking across Europe would be a starting point in conversations, with anyone interested in attempting to form a lasting relationship with me. And that’s the point of this long introductory statement.

As for why I'm here ... 
Actually I am looking for a real relationship.

I'm tired of dating sites where women show their cleavage or their butts and then ask for money or only want to chat online.

I'm looking for real. A real woman. A real love. A real life in what time is left to me.

If you'd be willing to meet face to face instead of chatting or messaging here, there would be a chance.

Three things that kill any attempt at starting a real relationship with me are these:

1) asking for money
2) sending nude photos by email
3) not being willing to meet face to face in a public, safe place.

I'm not bitter or angry, as some of the women seem to think, just cautious since I was scammed back in 2017 trying to find that one real woman.

I've said in before but no one seems to hear:
finding real love isn't like searching for a needle in a haystack - - -

it's like searching for a needle in a haystack size pile of needles and finding love is like finding that one 'golden' needle in a pile of needles as big as the haystacks in fairy tales.

Busco una dama madura que desee una relación tranquila, dispuesta a compartir y pasarla bien. Educada, culta, con buen léxico y humildad; esto no tiene nada que ver con la condición social. description:
Hello to all the sincere gentlemen of the world! I am beautiful, sensual, yet classy and playful. I have lived and loved, I have experienced great joy and great sorrow. Although a widow, it does not define me. I learn from my past and love with great faithfulness. I am a very proud mother, an adult daughter, and love my family. I have the gift of instruction, as I teach in my profession.
My hobbies are varied but fulfilling, ranging from preparing fine dishes to eat, or embroidering creative designs. Travel is one of my favorite activities, and it is something I wish to do more of. I live a very healthy lifestyle, and have absolutely zero addictions. I am strictly a one man kind of woman...faithful, loyal amd honest to a fault. I try to see the best in people, but am not easily fo
I seek a man that understands the words: monogamy, loyalty, faithfulness and honesty and respect. A man that also had raised a family is best, and a man that embraces a healthy lifestyle with no addictions. He must love to explore, travel is one of his hobbies, and being heslthy, keeps his body in top form, as I do. Above all, he seeks a true, lasting, long-term relationship that hopefully lasts a lifetime. I do NOT seek a pen friend, text buddy or sexting partner. Immaturity is not attractive. Let us build from a wonderful friendship that goes right into a loving and exciting life together!

name: Varsariah
description:
Soy un aprendis de escritor. Escribo a la vida lo que he callado por tanto tiempo. Dejo que mi corazón ejerza su derecho a expresarse. Aquí escribo mis pensamientos, cosas que me preocupan, algunas vivencias, historias que conozco... lo que me dicta el corazón para compartirlo con otras personas, es una manera de saber que no estamos solos en este mundo virtual y poder hacerlo más real y cercano. Me gusta escribir y me siento bien haciéndolo, ojalá estas letras lleguen a ustedes como yo quisiera. 

Con el paso del tiempo he aprendido, amanecer tras amanecer, tras muchos amaneceres en estos años de vueltas alrededor del sol, a poner las cosas en su sitio, a sembrar estas pisadas de crecimiento, a dejar que la oscuridad ciegue otras miradas, si están empeñadas en ello, sin dejar enturbiar la mía. Y no es perfecta mi vida, ¿hay perfección? No y sería aburrido.La mía no lo es, por supuesto, porque vivo en medio de todos, pero me levanto tras cada caída, me reinvento a mí mismo, hago de cada caída o tropiezo una oportunidad para ver en qué puedo mejorar y seguir adelante, una y otra vez, no es que sea fácil ni difícil, pero creo que es la única y máxima responsabilidad para con nosotros mismos. 

Tanto que el planeta anda obsesionado por el qué dirán los demás, cuando solamente debiera preocuparnos y ocuparnos el darnos cuentas a nosotros mismos, en lo que nuestra conciencia nos diga.

name: WhiteAndNerdy
description:
Part time dad of 2 boys, long-time geek, up for anything but I'm happiest just hanging out. Drink rarely, smoke routinely, eat bacon often, live on caffeine. Collector of pointless facts and surface-level understanding of many, many topics. Love a good conversation, especially if we can challenge each other.

Smart is sexy, talk nerdy to me... just don't expect me to understand Klingon. Picard over Kirk... but my favorite captain will always be Sam Carter.

If you're honest, a little funny and you can hold up your end of the conversation we'll do just fine. I'm a tactile person though and intimacy is definitely on my list of best things. If you like snuggling in front of a movie, holding hands in public, spooning, casual contact when we pass in the kitchen, cuddles after sex, being really close to someone just because... talk to me. If not, maybe I'm not what you're looking for. I'm not just here for NSA or FWB - I'm looking for more than that.

I'm young at heart and am told I don't look (or act) my age. I can do serious, just not all the time please.

And if you can't show an honest photo on your profile, why are you even here? Turn off the stupid filters, show us the real you. Take of the sunglasses and let us see your eyes. Show me the lines you get when you smile, they're part of who you are. Be real, or be a disappointment. We all have imperfections. Only cartoon characters and fake people are flawless, and neither of those are attractive.
